stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Inputting : User Text Entry
    Inputting --> Parsing : Submit Command
    Parsing --> Review : AI Success
    Parsing --> Error : AI Failure
    Error --> Inputting : Retry
    Review --> Saving : Confirm
    Review --> Inputting : Edit
    Saving --> Saved : DB Insert Success
    Saved --> Idle : View Dashboard
    Saving --> Error : DB Error
